{
  "schema": "reasoning_router_secrets_local_v1",
  "contract_version": 1,
  "_note": "Adapter reads OPENAI_API_KEY from the process environment only (no keys in this repo). On clawbot you may keep a **host-only** file outside the tree, e.g. ``~/.blackbox_secrets/openai.env`` (``chmod 600``) with ``export OPENAI_API_KEY='...'``; run ``source ~/.blackbox_secrets/openai.env`` in the same shell before pytest/Flask, or point systemd ``EnvironmentFile=`` at a file using ``KEY=value`` lines (no ``export``). This JSON is not read by the adapter."
}
